column1: Values for Belgium 1961-1999 and Luxembourg 1961-1999 are taken from a combined Belgium-Luxembourg time series.
Values for Czech Republic and Slovakia 1961-1990 are taken from a combined Czechoslovakia time series.
Values for Serbia and Montenegro 1991-2005 are taken from a combined Serbia & Montenegro time series.
Values for Bosnia & Herzegovina, Croatia, Macedonia, Montenegro, Serbia, and Slovenia 1961-1990 are taken from Yugoslav SFR.
Values for Belarus, Estonia, Latvia, Lithuania, Russia, and the Ukraine 1961-1990 are taken from USSR.
